	" is a crossword puzzle game for the Commodore 64 that was published in the February 1986 issue of the 
	[em 
		"Compute's Gazette
	]em
	". There are three difficulties: Level 1 has words formed horizontally and vertically, Level 2 adds reverse order, and Level 3 adds words that are formed diagonally. The game is over when all the words in the puzzle have been found.
